1.	 Follow the activate your account link in your welcome mail.  Also take note of the Cloud Account name as highlighted below 


 



Set a new password which meets the Password Criteria  




You will land on the Identity Cloud Service home page after successfully creating your new password

 



You have not been assigned any apps yet so you will need to provision an instance of Self Service Integration Cloud Service (SSI) next.

To do this, browse to http://cloud.oracle.com and click on the Sign In link


 

Enter in your cloud account from your original Welcome email.

 

     
